tasx is a web application for managing tasks. It is a test project for
learning the Groovy language and the Grails framework. A user of of tasx can:

* create account
* login
* create a task
* view account
* view tasks
* modify account
* modify a task
* delete account
* delete a task
* logout

A user has a name, an email address, a password, and a list of tasks. A task
has a plain-text description, a schedule, an integral priority, a status, and
zero or more subtasks. tasx will display a list of tasks sorted by date or
importance.